2020-07-07 Sébastien Millet <milletseb@laposte.net>

	* aa.sh: now uses reflector to build mirrorlist
			 Updating existing mirrorlist file was not possible any longer (if
			 keeping the logic of filtering by countr) as the file content
			 contains no more comments with country.

	* aa.sh: pacman -S doesn't use --noconfirm option any longer.
			 This option is a bit risky, sometimes useful options show up and
			 enforcing a default response is not ideal (yes, I'm now sticking
			 to the Arch way ;-) ).

	* aa.sh: creates an empty ~/.zshrc to avoid question at first zsh run

